General Assembly Proposed Bill No. 207
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 81
Referred to Committee on FINANCE, REVENUE AND
BONDING
Introduced by:
SEN. RAHMAN, 4th Dist.
AN ACT EXEMPTING OVERTIME INCOME FROM THE PERSONAL
INCOME TAX.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 That the general statutes be amended to exempt from the personal
2 income tax the amount of any overtime income earned by an employee.
Statement of Purpose:
To exempt from the personal income tax the amount of any overtime
income earned by an employee.
LCO No. 81 1 of 1

